707229f-a.title: Brooklyn: Voorhies Ave. - Bragg St.
707229f-a.text:
Voorhies Ave., north side, east from Bragg Street in foreground (not
visible). At the left was erected a sewage plant for Sheepshead Bay area.
July 7, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
